h3. Summary

This can be hard to replicate and does not happen every time, but there are a few reports of NPE happening in this call. This may happen during a re-index seems to correct itself after the index is done. Dashboard gadgets and the navigator are affected *for some users* until this reference does not produce a NPE.
h3. Expected Results

JIRA gracefully handles these issues.
h3. Actual Results

The below exception is thrown in the xxxxxxx.log file:
{noformat}
http-nio-8080-exec-224 ERROR USER 478x3239270x4 /rest/issueNav/1/issueTable [c.atlassian.velocity.DefaultVelocityManager] MethodInvocationException occurred getting message body from Velocity: java.lang.NullPointerException
java.lang.NullPointerException
	at com.atlassian.jira.issue.fields.SummarySystemField.populateVelocityParams(SummarySystemField.java:71)
	at com.atlassian.jira.issue.fields.AbstractTextSystemField.getColumnViewHtml(AbstractTextSystemField.java:59)
	at com.atlassian.jira.issue.fields.layout.column.ColumnLayoutItemImpl.getHtml(ColumnLayoutItemImpl.java:106)
	at sun.reflect.GeneratedMethodAccessor1837.invoke(Unknown Source)
{noformat}
h3. Notes

Looking at the code on the *SummarySystemField.java* class, it seems that the NPE error occurs when JIRA is attempting to get the parent key of a sub-task. Maybe there we can handle this more gracefully without affecting the navigator or dashboard gadgets.

{color:#d04437}*NPE Here*{color}
{code:java}
65    protected void populateVelocityParams(FieldLayoutItem fieldLayoutItem, Issue issue, Map<String, Object> params) {
66        super.populateVelocityParams(fieldLayoutItem, issue, params);
67        if (issue.isSubTask()) {
68            params.put("subTask", Boolean.TRUE);
69            Issue parentIssue = issue.getParentObject();
70            // do they have permission to see the parent issue, if not just show the key and not the summary
71            params.put("parentIssueKey", parentIssue.getKey());                             <-- line 71
72            params.put("subTaskParentIssueLinkDisabled", Boolean.TRUE);
73            if (getPermissionManager().hasPermission(Permissions.BROWSE, parentIssue, getAuthenticationContext().getUser())) {
74                params.put("parentIssueSummary", parentIssue.getSummary());
75                params.put("subTaskParentIssueLinkDisabled", Boolean.FALSE);
76            }
77        }
78    }{code}
